1. nslookup   bits-pilani.ac.in  a0.in.afilias-nst.info
> looks up A record for bits-pilani.ac.in using TLD server a0.in.afilias-nst.info

2. nslookup google.com
> looks up A record for google.com

3. nslookup -type=NS google.com
> looks up NS record for google.com

4. nslookup  google.com  ns2.google.com
> looks up A record for bits-pilani.ac.in using authoritative server ns2.google.com

5. nslookup  8.8.8.8
> reverse lookup, returns host name

6. nslookup   bits-pilani.ac.in   google-public-dns-a.google.com
> looks up A record for bits-pilani.ac.in using DNS server google-public-dns-a.google.com